      Allows a user to updated shared teacher's permissions on a run The user specified must exist, must have a ROLE_TEACHER, and must already be a shared owner of the run The invoker of this method must either: 1) have a ROLE_TEACHER authority and be the owner of the run 2) have a ROLE_ADMINISTRATOR The shared teacher will have the ROLES defined in the roles parameter.
